videos.description: Daniel Norl drives left and adjusts his body to finish the nice bucket.
videos.headline: Omaha's Norl finishes strong at the basket

videos.description: After a Louisville made a basket, Matt Pile races down the floor for the outlet pass and throws down the two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Omaha's Pile beats the defender for the slam

videos.description: Deng Adel jumps in the passing lane and finishes with a nice one-handed jam.
videos.headline: Louisville's Adel with the steal and flush

videos.description: Darius Perry shows great instincts to steal the ball, then cruises down the floor and finishes with an easy dunk.
videos.headline: Louisville's Perry turning defense into offense

videos.description: V.J. King runs down the floor and rises up for the alley-oop but it rattles out for the miss.
videos.headline: Louisville's King misses dunk

videos.description: After Quentin Snider's missed shot, Ray Spalding comes in for the tip-slam.
videos.headline: Loiusville's Spalding gets in great position for the jam
